v0.28 Episode 6 - 1st part (Act 2 begins)
---------------------------------------------------------------------
+ ADDED:
  • Episode 6 released with 225 new renders
  • 14 new animations
  • 2 new achievements for Episode 6
  • Walkthrough updated for Episode 6 decisions
  • 7 new comprehensive system documentation files (Achievements, Audio,
    Character Info, Core Systems, Notifications, Phone, Stats Screen)
  • Migration of save data for new systems
  • New story path begins (Act 2 storyline)
  • New character interactions and scenes

~ CHANGED:
  • Episode title backgrounds now fully animated
  • All achievements remade and re-rendered in 8K UHD (7680x4320)
  • Achievement images optimized for high-resolution displays
  • Character relationship tracking system enhanced
  • All walkthrough points updated to reflect new point system
  • GUI elements refined for better user experience
  • Animated transitions for episode titles improved

! FIXED:
  • 01 render corrected from version 0.27
  • Achievement screen zoom and drag functionality fixed for 8K UHD images
  • Zoom now centers at mouse position (mousewheel support added)
  • Drag constraints prevent showing empty background
  • Achievement display scaling fixed (base zoom 0.25 for 8K images)

* TECHNICAL:
  • Updated to Ren'Py 8.5
  • Changed webm codec to libaom-av1 for better compression
  • Achievement screen now supports 7680x4320 images with proper scaling
  • Added ZoomAtMouse class for smooth zoom functionality
  • Implemented constrain_offsets function for proper image boundaries
  • Episode 6 codebase: 2,635 lines (ep06.rpy), 234 lines (ep06_images.rpy),
    46 lines (ep06_vars.rpy)
  • Total code changes: ~25,850 insertions, ~39,416 deletions


